text: Puneet Kumar (born 22 June 1998) is an Indian cricketer. He made his List A debut for Jammu & Kashmir in the 2017–18 Vijay Hazare Trophy on 12 February 2018. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Indian cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Jammu and Kashmir cricketers
